query:
SELECT accountId, COUNT(*) as recordCount, 
       SUM(spend) as totalSpend, 
       SUM(sales) as totalSales,
       MIN(date) as minDate,
       MAX(date) as maxDate
FROM daily_performance 
GROUP BY accountId;
